### Linear CLI

A `linear` CLI is available on the server for all Linear operations. Use this instead of raw curl/GraphQL.

```bash
# Create an issue
linear issue create --title "..." --body "..." --label "Agent Handoff" --state Todo

# List issues
linear issue list [--limit 10]

# Show issue details
linear issue show {{LINEAR_TEAM_KEY}}-93

# Add a comment (posts as {{PROJECT_DISPLAY_NAME}} Agents by default)
linear comment add {{LINEAR_TEAM_KEY}}-93 "comment body"

# Add a comment as the main user
linear comment add {{LINEAR_TEAM_KEY}}-93 "comment body" --as-user

# List comments
linear comment list {{LINEAR_TEAM_KEY}}-93

# JSON output (all commands)
linear issue list --json
```

Config: `{{SERVER_HOME}}/tools/linear-cli/.env`
Docs: `{{SERVER_HOME}}/tools/linear-cli/AGENTS.md`

For the GM creating issues during delivery, use the CLI via SSH:
```bash
ssh {{SERVER_HOST}} "export PATH={{SERVER_HOME}}/bin:...\$PATH && linear issue create --title '...' --body '...' --label 'Agent Handoff' --state Todo"
```

See also delivery-workflow.md in memory for full delivery process details.
{{/LINEAR}}

