### Cloudflare R2 (Asset Hosting)

All deliverable assets (images, files) must be uploaded to R2 for public access.

```
Bucket: {{R2_BUCKET}}
Public URL base: {{R2_PUBLIC_URL}}/
Upload tool: wrangler (must use --remote flag, requires wrangler.toml in cwd)
wrangler.toml location: {{LOCAL_PROJECT_DIR}}/tmp/wrangler.toml
```

Upload command:
```bash
cd {{LOCAL_PROJECT_DIR}}/tmp && wrangler r2 object put "{{R2_BUCKET}}/<path>/<filename>" --remote --file "<local-path>" --content-type "image/jpeg"
```

Public URL pattern: `{{R2_PUBLIC_URL}}/<path>/<filename>`
{{/R2}}

